Title: Death of the Doctor (1)
Plot: Old Companions Sarah Jane Smith and Jo Grant meet for the first time to discover the truth when the Doctor is declared dead. An interstellar conspiracy gathers around UNIT Head Quarters as Clyde finds that he holds the fate of the Time Lord in his hand.
GuestStars: Matt Smith, Katy Manning, Finn Jones, Laila Rouass, Ace Bhatti, Jimmy Vee, Phillip Hurd-Wood, David Bradley, Jon Glover, Paul Kasey, Rauri Mears, Ben Ashley
